A '''Geonym''' is a [[name]] of a [[geography|geographical]] feature. The term covers everything, from names of [[continent]]s to those of the smallest [[Hamlet (place)|hamlet]]s. Each [[toponym]], [[hydronym]], and so on is a geonym.

